{"tid":2354603,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共產黨：黨開始無錢啦 不過會緊縮開支 讓人民過上好日子","createTime":"2021-01-05T15:01:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T15:06:44.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f1fb0a84651e51fa37683d6658971dd8c578aab4","tid":2354603,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T15:01:22.000Z","msg":"財長劉昆：新一年政府要過緊日子<br />\n<br />\n國家財政部長劉昆表示，新一年政府要過「緊日子」，讓人民過上好日子，強調財政收支壓力再大，也要堅決保障好民生支出。他說，支出規模和政策力度要保持基本穩定，為今後應對新的風險挑戰留出政策空間。今年預算安排將一如既往加強對地方的財力保障，優先安排好保基本民生、保工資、保運轉壓力加大的「三保」支出。<br />\n<br />\n劉昆又指，去年連續發佈實施28項減稅降費政策，全年規模預計超過2.5萬億元人民幣，「十三五」時期累計減稅降費規模達到7.6萬億元左右。另外，去年財政直達資金預算下達已經完成，截至去年12月29日，1.52萬億元已經投入使用；今年直達資金總量將比去年有所增加，範圍擴大。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/china/2373560\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F2373560&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAG73SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=8cd5c59f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/china/2373560</a>"},{"pid":"01f9994d68cba6baed4a4b6d96a1fdfe8394ec4e","tid":2354603,"uid":294343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T15:02:26.000Z","msg":"不可能，中國是宇宙無敵"},{"pid":"90fcfa5db3a6ef4174c3a8e1729bba28bbca8281","tid":2354603,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T15:03:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"341b9f76cf66367f47cd2bc5f6c65dd43e28e2c2","tid":2354603,"uid":35580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T15:06:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />jack媽"},{"pid":"8f8e453f506914d9be00161dcca7e5111e880202","tid":2354603,"uid":40272,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T15:06:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/86gNHRS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F86gNHRS.gif&h=d1eb300f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}